    "title": "Focaccia Is Easier Than You Think",
    "language": "en",
    "description": "Head to https://squarespace.com/andycooks to save 10% off your first purchase of a website or domain using ANDYCOOKS !\n\nFocaccia is one of my favourite kinds of bread, and it’s a lot easier to make than you think! In this video I’ll go in depth on how to nail your dough every time, and I’ll also show you some ways to turn your focaccia into something special.\n\nCheck out SolSnack here: https://www.youtube.com/@SolSnack\n\nMY PRODUCTS: https://bit.ly/AndyCooksEssentials\nMY COOKBOOK: https://bit.ly/3WVoXAN\n\nRECIPES:\nFocaccia: https://www.andy-cooks.com/blogs/recipes/no-knead-focaccia\nLemon, olive and oregano: https://www.andy-cooks.com/blogs/recipes/lemon-olive-and-oregano-focaccia\nGrandma Pie: https://www.andy-cooks.com/blogs/recipes/grandma-pie\n\nTIMESTAMPS:\n\n00:00 Intro\n00:34 Plain Focaccia\n15:40 Chicken Stock Focaccia\n19:42 Lemon, olive and oregano focaccia \n24:06 Sorta Sicillian Pizza \n\nFOLLOW ME:\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/andyhearnden\nTikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@andy_cooks\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/andy.h.cooks\nWebsite with all my recipes: https://www.andy-cooks.com/\n\nPot wash: Andy\nProducer: Caleb Dawkins\nVideographer: Ben Hasic\nEditor: Liam Craig",
