        "text": "Cover the dough with a tea towel and let it rest for another 30 minutes. Repeat this process three more times.",
        "language": "en",
        "timerSeconds": 1800,
        "mediaAnchors": [
          {
            "sourceId": "source-0c325bed-9276-4881-a863-fd1cbe9152f3",
